SEARCH

Uses of Package
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.events

Packages that use nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.events
Package
Description
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.api.factories
This package contains various factories for creating objects used in the project.
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.commands
This package contains command definitions and command factories used by this project, as well as various base command classes and interfaces.
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.events
Contains interfaces and classes for handling events related to AnimatedArchitecture structures.
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.managers
This package contains managers that manage different certain aspects of the plugin.
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.moveblocks
This package contains the core logic for animating structures..
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures
This package contains classes that define, manipulate, and manage structures.
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.core.events
This package contains implementations for all event-related classes for the AnimatedArchitecture plugin for the Spigot platform as well as utilities to call events.
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.core.implementations
This package contains classes that provide implementations for various interfaces in the core module for the Spigot platform.
  • Classes in nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.events used by nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.api.factories
    Class
    Description
    IStructureCreatedEvent
    Represents the event where a structure was created.
    IStructureEventToggleEnd
    Represents a toggle action that has been applied to a structure.
    IStructureEventTogglePrepare
    Represents a toggle action that might be applied to a structure.
    IStructureEventToggleStart
    Represents a toggle action that will be applied to a structure.If you want to cancel the action, use IStructureEventTogglePrepare instead.
    IStructurePrepareAddOwnerEvent
    Represents the event where a new owner is added to a structure.
    IStructurePrepareCreateEvent
    Represents the event where a structure will be created.
    IStructurePrepareDeleteEvent
    Represents the event where a structure was deleted.
    IStructurePrepareLockChangeEvent
    Represents the event where a structure will be (un)locked.
    IStructurePrepareRemoveOwnerEvent
    Represents the event where an owner is removed from a structure.
    StructureActionCause
    Represents the different kind of causes that can be the reason of a AbstractStructure action.
    StructureActionType
    Represents the different kinds of actions that are applicable to a structure.
